#: ../../P/point-and-drool-interface.rst:9
msgid ""
"Parody of the techspeak term point-and-click interface, describing a "
"windows, icons, and mouse-based interface such as is found on the Macintosh."
" The implication, of course, is that such an interface is only suitable for "
"idiots. See :ref:`for-the-rest-of-us`\\, :ref:`WIMP-environment`\\, "
":ref:`Macintrash`\\, :ref:`drool-proof-paper`\\. Also point-and-grunt "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"Macintoshに見られるような、ウィンドウ、アイコン、マウスベースのインターフェースを表す、技術用語point-and-click "
"interfaceのパロディ。もちろんその含みは、そのようなインターフェースは馬鹿にしか向いていないということである。\\ :ref:`for-the-"
"rest-of-us`\\ 、\\ :ref:`WIMP-environment`\\ 、\\ :ref:`Macintrash`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`drool-proof-paper`\\ を参照。point-and-grunt interfaceとも。"
